### Overview

Built with industrial-grade reliability, the **IoTextra Combo** features a high-resolution **ADS1115 ADC** and robust **galvanic isolation**, making it an ideal bridge between low-voltage digital logic and high-voltage loads.

This hybrid design enables both **precise analog sensing** and **reliable power switching** within a single compact module, simplifying system design and installation.

